        <mxCell id="jqg2egQ6bgCff2YKCfo0-99" value="&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 15px;&quot; color=&quot;#3399ff&quot;&gt;Script Data Tag（控制帧）&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="4088.5" y="119.99999999999989" width="210" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="jqg2egQ6bgCff2YKCfo0-100" value="AMF1(&#39;onMetaData&#39;)" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="4097.5" y="179.2600000000001" width="552" height="30.88" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="jqg2egQ6bgCff2YKCfo0-102" value="&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; float: none; display: inline !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Script Data Tags通常用来存放跟FLV中音视频相关的元数据信息（onMetaData），比如时长、长度、宽度等。它的定义相对复杂些，采用AMF（Action Message Format）封装了一系列数据类型，比如字符串、数值、数组等。&lt;/span&gt;通常该类型Tag会跟在File Header后面作为第一个Tag出现，而且只有一个。&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="4278.5" y="119.99999999999989" width="590" height="39.26" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="jqg2egQ6bgCff2YKCfo0-103" value="AMF1(&#39;height width...&#39;)" style="whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="4649.5" y="179.2600000000001" width="552" height="30.88" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="jqg2egQ6bgCff2YKCfo0-104" value="" style="shape=image;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;labelBackgroundColor=default;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/png,;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="5221.5" y="279.2600000000001" width="429" height="210.2" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="jqg2egQ6bgCff2YKCfo0-105" value="" style="shape=image;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;labelBackgroundColor=default;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/png,;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="5201.5" y="560.0000000000001" width="718" height="366.17" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="jqg2egQ6bgCff2YKCfo0-106" value="&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;onMetaData中包含了音视频相关的元数据，封装在Script Data Tag中，它包含了两个AMF。&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;第一个AMF：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;第1个字节：0x02，表示字符串类型&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;第2-3个字节：UI16类型，值为0x000A，表示字符串的长度为10（onMetaData的长度）；&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;第4-13个字节：字符串onMetaData对应的16进制数字（0x6F 0x6E 0x4D 0x65 0x74 0x61 0x44 0x61 0x74 0x61）；&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;第二个AMF：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;第1个字节：0x08，表示数组类型；&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;第2-5个字节：UI32类型，表示数组的长度，onMetaData中具体包含哪些属性是不固定的。&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;第6个字节+：比如duration，则：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;margin: 0px 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: circle;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;第6-9个字节：0x0008，表示长度为8个字节；&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;第10-17个字节：0x6475 7261 7469，表示 duration 这个字符串；&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;第18个字节：0x00，表示为数值类型；&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: inherit;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;第19-26个字节：0x...，表示具体的时长；&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="4108.5" y="219.2600000000001" width="560" height="390" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
